        <p>There is a check box in the Options dialog that lets you dictate what happens when you have multiple identical source terms and you begin translating, confirming, and uploading them to translation memory (TM). After segments are confirmed, what happens to those that are not yet translated? Are translations for those segments updated accordingly? That's what this check box lets you control.</p>
